{"tid":55176,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"推薦套設定幾好既冒險漫畫-來自深淵","createTime":"2016-12-26T07:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T14:47:44.000Z","uid":8307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"954fcc612bd051071091ff318dcbd0c7127dc9ff","tid":55176,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qjzh910f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqjzh910f&h=26bdcde9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n套野就用正太蘿莉畫風既角色做主角<br />\n本漫畫畫面畫得好細緻好靚,可以上PIXIV試睇下作者既畫<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=4886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fmember.php%3Fid%3D4886&d=Biu%2F91mHmctbe3AtVN6d%2BQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=35dda319\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=4886</a><br />\n<br />\n來自深淵起始劇情有少少似近年都幾受歡迎既漫畫黃金神威,大概講述男女主要去某個地方中途又打下獵煮下野食咁<br />\n主線就一陣先講講下個設定先,會睇啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來自深淵設定係話,係呢個世界上有一個窿,啲人就叫佢做ABYSS深淵<br />\n就話呢個窿入面有各種神奇既生物,同埋各種神奇既物品道具叫做 遺物<br />\n所以世界上既探險隊都黎到呢個窿探險<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/revdfkqb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frevdfkqb&h=6db6425f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實探險呢個窿就好危險,首先就有唔同危險既生物,例如有啲寄生你既肉體,令你半殘,方便佢地吸引養份同繁值<br />\n除此之外,你有危險都唔可以向上爬,因為設定上係深淵入面,有一種上升既詛咒<br />\n<br />\n呢段就copy返黎<br />\n第一層：輕微的眩暈、嘔吐<br />\n第二層：頭痛、嚴重嘔吐、肢體末端麻痺<br />\n第三層：平衡感失常、幻覺及幻聽<br />\n第四層：全身激痛，七孔流血<br />\n第五層：全身的感覺喪失，意識混濁、自傷行為<br />\n第六層：喪失人性，或是死亡<br />\n第七層：確實的死亡<br />\n奈落之底：未知<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你唔小心爬下樓梯,行下山都可能會瓜<br />\n<br />\n除此之外,冒險家亦都分為唔同等級<br />\n初初接受訓練就叫 持鈴生 ,通常係孤兒,因為父母係冒險家,所以就想做<br />\n之後就分 赤笛,蒼笛,月笛,黑笛 同 白笛 分別就係可以深淵活動既層數(1-5層,因為6層之後上返黎會死)<br />\n白笛就係最勁,亦都係最少人做到,但係白笛有啲癡線佬就落去6層樓下唔上返黎<br />\n某位白笛,睇下幾有型,唔係淨係得可愛畫風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女女都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0pl38o1q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0pl38o1q&h=b63cea29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vpo6nyqd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvpo6nyqd&h=5312c9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n表面上睇套野好似用可愛畫風,既冒險漫畫,實際上套野都有些少黑暗扭曲,例如話有啲生物食完人肉,人類都照樣食返佢<br />\n用細路仔做人體實驗方便自己探索深淵之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae8f20a65a580f4da4811e0c1e1a2e1b2414121","tid":55176,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:51:22.000Z","msg":"tldr<br />\n但會睇 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645742995e8035b383dd93631585e034c2f09ed8","tid":55176,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>tldr<br />\n但會睇 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n圖長姐,得幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe74987f8c951de8c5f9e78ec26697e414411c5","tid":55176,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"茅人理"},{"pid":"b6625485b22e88756cac654f81384b16197c55cd","tid":55176,"uid":43213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茅人理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇完簡介幾吸引 會睇下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291cd567f86d2cf8f0fd3411efb97970e0b15dc6","tid":55176,"uid":23751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:36:53.000Z","msg":"娜娜奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebf308852a319b264686e46ac40aff388da0d31","tid":55176,"uid":65777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:46:21.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"08689bd4f3bd72a524b2a9f032951f0383af3402","tid":55176,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-